snippet: Former world sprint champion Tyson Gay will return from a one-year doping suspension at next month's Lausanne Diamond League meeting, organizers said on Monday....

headline.print_headline: Banned U.S. Sprinter Gay to Make Return in Lausanne
headline.main: Banned U.S. Sprinter Gay to Make Return in Lausanne

lead_paragraph: Former world sprint champion Tyson Gay will return from a one-year doping suspension at next month's Lausanne Diamond League meeting, organizers said on Monday.
